{"tid":2131052,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"黃色經濟正面臨崩潰？不如整翻個黃店外賣app","createTime":"2020-07-29T14:36:36.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-29T17:29:30.000Z","uid":256266,"like":30,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"f8aa7ddcbed11994dabe499f3eb0b3441f87e8fd","tid":2131052,"uid":256266,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T14:36:36.000Z","msg":"有冇覺得而家想幫襯黃店冇之前咁方便<br />\n之前都仲話一行街見到某D標誌就知可以入去食<br />\n而家和你eat冇左 文宣冇左<br />\n家下仲冇左堂食 好多黃店都經營有困難<br />\n而家仲出現左好多黃外賣<br />\n如果有一個app可以整合哂所有<br />\n一打開就可以直接簡食咩<br />\n唔使上網左揾右揾<br />\n又唔會變左大家整係食死幾間出名黃店 可以平均分配<br />\n啲淺黃又唔會大把籍口 話都唔知邊到有麻鬼煩<br />\n我成日覺得黃色經濟圈最大嘅缺點就係互相合作唔多 都係你有你做 我有我做 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果有一個平台 可以聯繫哂黃店<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁樣黃店 黃色經濟圈先可以成長 壯大<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n <br />\n小妹不才冇咩能力 只係想從一個消費者嘅角度去發表一下意見"},{"pid":"c3678854a8fc2fad909e780e9708f26221eb76ef","tid":2131052,"uid":38904,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T14:37:29.000Z","msg":"lingduck?"},{"pid":"0d8e6b081766291ebb56e05e428fb2e6b0a5be54","tid":2131052,"uid":256266,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"c3678854a8fc2fad909e780e9708f26221eb76ef","tid":2131052,"uid":38904,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T14:37:29.000Z","msg":"lingduck?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T14:42:36.000Z","msg":"Yes 不過入面如果可以有埋黃外送會更好<br />\nBtw呢個app唔係好多人知<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/on_hold.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我好多friend 都唔知<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df8eb3f618a988409e048b09eb1fe9425dc8420b","tid":2131052,"uid":286155,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T14:44:05.000Z","msg":"點解區區都有，唔直接整合做個大app"},{"pid":"e7c0dd25cc1a6182a21914649b68f922149243ff","tid":2131052,"uid":256266,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"